@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ntmfwe(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (v0 - wp.cos((tmp + 0.65 - v2 + 0.24)))
    v0 = (0.77 * 0.61)
    v0 = (wp.sin(0.02) - (tmp * wp.sin(v1 + 0.54)))
    v1 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
